{
  "1808680": {
    "name": "《史力奇奇遇记：姆明山谷之歌》",
    "steam_appid": 1808680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808680/extras/6873950e47441fbef90bbefc9fc3a7a5.avif?t=1768898556\" width=616 height=190 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《史力奇奇遇记：姆明山谷之歌》是一款剧情与音乐交织的冒险游戏。姆明山谷中住着许多让人过目难忘的奇趣角色和小动物，与自然景致和谐共处，没想到在姆明谷出现了一系列奇特的公园，破坏了这片土地的景观和和谐的自然环境。——此时，身为史力奇的你需挺身而出，想尽办法引开警官，拽倒错误的指示，推翻格格不入的雕塑，给公园管理员的大改造计划画上句点，还山谷中住民一个生机盎然的家园……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 你将畅游托芙·扬松妙笔铸就的姆明世界，故事生动、情感细腻，再加一抹淡淡的愁绪，为本作注入精致灵动的北欧气息。开放世界、解谜机制、谨慎潜行、美妙旋律……种种元素合而为一，打造出适合全年龄段玩家的治愈之旅！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808680/extras/b9b7a44c09d9856d97e11dd008930f02.poster.avif?t=1768898556\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808680/extras/b9b7a44c09d9856d97e11dd008930f02.webm?t=1768898556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  绘本世界，活灵活现</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 眼前的世界颇得姆明故事之精髓，奇思妙想层出不穷，原本存在于绘本和动画中的景象生动铺陈，带给你前所未有的沉浸式体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《史力奇奇遇记：姆明山谷之歌》的配乐是由冰岛后摇乐队 Sigur Rós 谱写，乐章中迈出轻快步伐，与美妙节奏同频共振。作为史力奇的你也可以吹响口琴，以乐交友，结识姆明山谷的住民。在这里，尽可以迈开步、放宽心，给精神减个负。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808680/extras/f7a633b4bb9e678ba26f0d0c0bc04eba.poster.avif?t=1768898556\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808680/extras/f7a633b4bb9e678ba26f0d0c0bc04eba.webm?t=1768898556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  各式角色，奇趣满分</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >姆明山谷中角色众多，每位的个性都鲜明又立体，值得层层深挖。在这趟旅途中，你不仅要探查一系列奇特的公园出现在此处的原因，也别忘了和别具魅力的姆明山谷住民做好友喔！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808680/extras/e3be4bf917dbb0a4e0cb9842ce60136f.poster.avif?t=1768898556\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808680/extras/e3be4bf917dbb0a4e0cb9842ce60136f.webm?t=1768898556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动人音乐伴旅途</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在这里，你能看到用地平线藏了半个身子，暖融融的琥珀色光芒泼向离离绿草的日落；也能感受到野花将清香织进微风，捎来不为人知的故事与奇闻。你将会化身史力奇，帽檐低垂，口琴在手，启程探索谜题重重的姆明山谷，寻觅灵感之光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 主要特色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  * 冒险之旅轻松惬意，丰富多彩，更有绘本般生动清新的艺术风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  * 用好手中的口琴，施加一点小小的潜行技巧，还有一路结交的好友助阵，足以把严苛的公园管理员和他那毫无美感的产物请出姆明山谷</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  * 姆明山谷中住着超过 50 位魅力十足的角色和生物，等你来结识</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  * 叙事贯穿游戏始终，串联起大量独具特色的剧情与任务，一切都与托芙·扬松笔下可爱的角色息息相关</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  * 穿梭于开放世界，解开与音乐和环境联系紧密的种种谜题，探寻谷中机密</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  * 沉浸式欣赏 Sigur Rós 带来的美妙音乐旋律</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808680/extras/6bf6a040c0ce758e867e1a81ef86545f.avif?t=1768898556\" width=616 height=262 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808680/extras/deb74f4835554bba3614a5103209d0b3.avif?t=1768898556\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >© Snufkin: Melody of Moominvalley. Developed by Hyper Games. Published by Raw Fury AB. © Moomin Characters ™</p>",
